[I] Collection of add-ons for the CMake build tool

[T] Collection of add-ons for the CMake build tool. Add-ons include
[T] for CopyrightTest, CoverageReport, DoxygenBuilder, FormatCode
[T] gcovr, GDbus, GMock, GSettings, IncludeChecker, Intltool, Lcov
[T] and QmlPlugins.

